# CODEOWNERS for haveebot/port-a-local
#
# Set alongside agent-driven contributor autonomy (2026-05-04).
# Branch protection requires status checks (Vercel build) but no
# general approving review. Code owner review IS required on the paths
# below — meaning sensitive surfaces still get operator eyes; cosmetic
# / brand / copy / component changes auto-merge once checks pass.
#
# Default (no codeowner): no review required — checks-only gate.

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Backend / API / data — operator review required
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
