# CI / Actions
/.github/workflows/             @haveebot @nickbmerrill-collab

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Free-merge surfaces (no codeowner = auto-merges on checks pass):
#   - app/(public)/**           Brand pages, marketing, public routes
#   - components/**             UI components
#   - styles/**, app/globals.css  Styling
#   - public/**                 Static assets, images
#   - content/**, docs/**       Editorial content + docs
#   - CONTRIBUTORS.md           Contributor list
